```mermaid
flowchart TD
    classDef pending fill:#555,stroke:#999,color:#fff
    classDef inprogress fill:#b8860b,stroke:#ffd700,color:#fff
    classDef done fill:#2d6a4f,stroke:#52b788,color:#fff
    classDef failed fill:#7f1d1d,stroke:#ef4444,color:#fff
    classDef skipped fill:#374151,stroke:#6b7280,color:#aaa

    T1["✓ #1: First task"]
    T2["○ #2: Second task"]

    T1 --> T2

    class T1 done
    class T2 pending
```
